                <head>67. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On November 12, Assistant Secretary <persName corresp="#p_RWM1"
                        >Rountree</persName> sent a memorandum to Secretary <persName
                        corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName> concerning the relationship between the
                    India-Pakistan disputes and a proposed economic aid program for India. This
                    memorandum is printed as <ref target="#d181">Document 181</ref>.</p>
            </div>
